import matplotlib.pyplot as plt 
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import numpy as np

print(pddf)

print(temp)

matrix = np.triu(temp.corr())

a=sns.heatmap(pddf.corr(), annot=True,  annot_kws={"size": 20},
